WEBVTT

00:00:00.520 --> 00:00:03.536
Chris Anderson:
Elon, hey, welcome back to TED.

00:00:03.560 --> 00:00:04.936
It's great to have you here.

00:00:04.960 --> 00:00:06.536
Elon Musk: Thanks for having me.

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:09.416
CA: So, in the next half hour or so,

00:00:09.440 --> 00:00:11.256
we're going to spend some time

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:15.176
exploring your vision for what
an exciting future might look like,

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:19.296
which I guess makes
the first question a little ironic:

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:21.056
Why are you boring?

00:00:21.080 --> 00:00:22.296
EM: Yeah.

00:00:22.320 --> 00:00:23.870
I ask myself that frequently.

